  • com.aylanetworks.agilelink使用的com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.change中的类 
    类和说明
    Change
    Change objects are provided to the application whenever the SDK has detected changes to objects, and the applicaiton has requested to listen for changes.
    ListChange
    A ListChange is issued when a list managed by the SDK has had items added or removed to or from it.

  • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk使用的com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.change中的类 
    类和说明
    Change
    Change objects are provided to the application whenever the SDK has detected changes to objects, and the applicaiton has requested to listen for changes.
    ListChange

    PropertyChange
    A PropertyChange is used to notify listeners of the details of a Device's property changing.
  • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.change使用的com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.change中的类 
    类和说明
    Change
    Change objects are provided to the application whenever the SDK has detected changes to objects, and the applicaiton has requested to listen for changes.
    Change.ChangeType
    Enumeration of the various types of changes that are reported by the Change objects.
    FieldChange
    A FieldChange object contains a list of the names of fields of an object that have changed.
